{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>去到灣仔告士打道5號對開時，警員截停保時捷，男司機即場進行酒精呼氣測試，結果顯示40多度，超出法定上限22度，警員以涉嫌「酒後駕駛」罪名作出拘捕，將被捕男子帶署作進一步調查，警員在車內沒有發現其他可疑物品。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127109317829332992849165.jpeg/UqA0ihdFruEKdqbCnBQyYc2k2EGCamyhGuIOdSDiDnU\" alt=\"警員在場調查。（李家傑攝）\"><figcaption>警員在場調查。（李家傑攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127109321809858560510937.jpeg/Hgv8shpKPWww_mZZemDh2kp-h-EVg-x-NoryDgyK8g4\" alt=\"圖為涉案自訂車牌的保時捷。（李家傑攝）\"><figcaption>圖為涉案自訂車牌的保時捷。（李家傑攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127109325467422720265813.jpeg/Vif2gblUTegbzEeOKCq_DpCG1aYZUpdHgOA1k7rgNZM\" alt=\"車內沒有發現其他可疑物品。（李家傑攝）\"><figcaption>車內沒有發現其他可疑物品。（李家傑攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T21:32:42.203877+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":157,"images":3,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}